      <trans-unit id="411214078788534097" datatype="html">
        <source>
Grew from intern to full-time developer over 3 years at a Paris health-tech startup, including a 6-month freelance/contractor period (Jan–Jun 2023) while working remotely from abroad.

&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-4&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Designed&lt;/span&gt; and maintained a centralized UI design system for consistency across applications.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-2&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Implemented&lt;/span&gt; CI/CD pipelines with Git, Docker, and Azure DevOps.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-2&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Built&lt;/span&gt; full-stack features with Vue.js/TypeScript on the frontend and NestJS/PostgreSQL on the backend.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-2&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Enhanced&lt;/span&gt; reliability with end-to-end and unit tests using Cypress and Jest.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-2&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Optimized&lt;/span&gt; service communication using proxy gateways and load balancers.&lt;/div&gt;
      </source>
        <target>
Progresé de becario a desarrollador a tiempo completo durante 3 años en una startup parisina de salud, con un período de 6 meses como freelance/contratista (ene–jun 2023) trabajando en remoto desde el extranjero.

&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-4&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Diseñé&lt;/span&gt; y mantuve un sistema de diseño UI centralizado para garantizar la coherencia entre aplicaciones.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-2&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Implementé&lt;/span&gt; pipelines CI/CD con Git, Docker y Azure DevOps.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-2&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Desarrollé&lt;/span&gt; funcionalidades full-stack con Vue.js/TypeScript en frontend y NestJS/PostgreSQL en backend.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-2&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Mejoré&lt;/span&gt; la fiabilidad con pruebas end-to-end y unitarias usando Cypress y Jest.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ms-4 mt-2&quot;&gt;• &lt;span class=&quot;font-medium&quot;&gt;Optimicé&lt;/span&gt; la comunicación entre servicios mediante proxy gateways y load balancers.&lt;/div&gt;
      </target>
